{"words":[{"word":"treasure","count":5},{"word":"give","count":4},{"word":"cause","count":4},{"word":"grand","count":4},{"word":"hahaha","count":4},{"word":"i'll","count":3},{"word":"show","count":2},{"word":"fools","count":2},{"word":"fine","count":2},{"word":"key","count":2},{"word":"must","count":2},{"word":"treasures","count":2},{"word":"wait","count":2},{"word":"crew","count":2},{"word":"life","count":2},{"word":"troupe","count":2},{"word":"true","count":2},{"word":"gold","count":2},{"word":"ano","count":2},{"word":"chop","count":2},{"word":"quite","count":2},{"word":"oh","count":2},{"word":"yes","count":2},{"word":"man","count":2},{"word":"first","count":2},{"word":"mine","count":2},{"word":"kill","count":1},{"word":"brant","count":1},{"word":"soon","count":1},{"word":"useless","count":1},{"word":"slow","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"resort","count":1},{"word":"t-to","count":1},{"word":"violence","count":1},{"word":"takes","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"keys","count":1},{"word":"unlock","count":1},{"word":"split","count":1},{"word":"sixty-forty","count":1},{"word":"i-i'll","count":1},{"word":"generous","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"sixty","count":1},{"word":"settle","count":1},{"word":"forty","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"poor","count":1},{"word":"souls","count":1},{"word":"deserve","count":1},{"word":"a-a","count":1},{"word":"happy","count":1},{"word":"peaceful","count":1},{"word":"captain","count":1},{"word":"fair","count":1},{"word":"deal","count":1},{"word":"agree","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"decision","count":1},{"word":"none","count":1},{"word":"gate's","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"claim","count":1},{"word":"ahhhh","count":1},{"word":"uh","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"defend","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"fool's","count":1},{"word":"farewell","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"dear","count":1},{"word":"friends","count":1},{"word":"joy","count":1},{"word":"piece","count":1},{"word":"i-i","count":1},{"word":"absolutely","count":1},{"word":"quaking","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"monster","count":1},{"word":"gives","count":1},{"word":"shivers","count":1},{"word":"finally","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"senses","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"alone","count":1},{"word":"unsettling","count":1},{"word":"took","count":1},{"word":"beast","count":1},{"word":"faster","count":1},{"word":"blink","count":1},{"word":"close","count":1},{"word":"realizing","count":1},{"word":"drake's","count":1},{"word":"brilliant","count":1},{"word":"so-so","count":1},{"word":"dazzling","count":1},{"word":"principle","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"hoard","count":1},{"word":"wealth","count":1},{"word":"spirit","count":1},{"word":"fairness","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"honor","count":1},{"word":"opening","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"ahead","count":1},{"word":"pick","count":1},{"word":"c-curse","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"fears","count":1},{"word":"mere","count":1},{"word":"legends","count":1},{"word":"offer","count":1},{"word":"comes","count":1},{"word":"straight","count":1},{"word":"heart","count":1},{"word":"hahahaha","count":1},{"word":"curse","count":1},{"word":"turns","count":1},{"word":"harmless","count":1},{"word":"kitten","count":1},{"word":"fretted","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"toss","count":1},{"word":"modest","count":1},{"word":"pouch","count":1},{"word":"loyal","count":1},{"word":"mateys","count":1},{"word":"rest","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"pilgrim's","count":1},{"word":"sail","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"stayed","count":1},{"word":"chase","count":1},{"word":"desires","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"chains","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"cracked","count":1},{"word":"code","count":1},{"word":"money","count":1},{"word":"calling","count":1},{"word":"wh-what","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"KILL THEM!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Brant. I didn't think you'd show up so soon.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"…Useless fools. Couldn't even slow you down.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Fine, you want the key, don't you? I could give it to you, but—","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"No, no! Must we always resort t-to violence? See that? It takes two keys to unlock!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"You have one, and I have the other.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"We both want the treasures, right? So how about this, I'll give you my key, but we split the treasure. Sixty-forty… No, wait, I-I'll be generous. You take the sixty, and I'll settle for forty.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"You've seen my crew. Those poor souls… I'm doing this for them, to give them the life they deserve. A-a happy, peaceful life.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"What do you say, Captain of the Troupe of Fools? A fair deal, wouldn't you agree?","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Come on, we don't have all day! Make a decision, or none of us will get the treasure!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Here you go. The gate's right over there.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Time to claim our treasures... Wait! What's that!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Ahhhh! You, uh, stay here and defend our great cause! Show them the true might of the Fool's Troupe. FAREWELL!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"The gold… My gold…","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Treasure… My grand cause… No…","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Ah, my dear friends! What a joy to see you both in one piece!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"I-I was absolutely quaking back there. Just the thought of that <ano=Chop Chop>monster</ano>… it still gives me the shivers!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"When I finally came to my senses, I found myself here, all alone. Quite... quite unsettling, I must say.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"But look at you! You took down that beast faster than I could blink.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Grand…? Oh yes! My grand cause! I'm this close to realizing it, you see. Look! Drake's treasure is right there, so brilliant, so-so dazzling…","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"But as a man of principle, I could never hoard such wealth all to myself.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"So, in the spirit of fairness, I'd like to give you the honor of opening it first. Please go ahead, the first pick is yours!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"C-curse? Hahaha! Do I look like the kind of man who fears mere legends? No, no, my offer comes straight from the heart.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"You... you look fine…","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Hahahaha! Curse? Turns out it's as harmless as a kitten!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"I fretted for nothing! Yes, now all this treasure is MINE!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Grand cause? My crew? Oh right…","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"I'll toss a modest pouch to each of my loyal mateys, and the rest? ALL MINE! Hahaha!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"When I left the Pilgrim's Sail, there was only one thing that stayed with me—to chase my desires without chains.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"And after all these years, I've cracked the code… Money! Hahaha! That's my one true calling. Hahaha!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Wh-what?!","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000}]}